From: Liu Ying <Ying.Liu@freescale.com>
Date: Tue, 25 Mar 2014 14:39:01 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 0348/1074] ENGR00305067-7 ARM: dts: imx6sx-sdb: Rename pwm3
 backlight node

This patch renames the backlight node based on pwm3 from 'backlight'
to 'backlight1' so that we may add the upcoming backlight node based
on pwm4 which is named to 'backlight2'.

Signed-off-by: Liu Ying <Ying.Liu@freescale.com>
[Original patch taken from git://git.freescale.com/imx/linux-2.6-imx.git]
Signed-off-by: Biyao Zhai <biyao.zhai@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dts |    2 +-
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 1 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dts b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dts
index 49e1c9a..add0d90 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dts
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6sx-sdb.dts
@@ -14,7 +14,7 @@
 	model = "Freescale i.MX6 SoloX SDB Board";
 	compatible = "fsl,imx6sx-sdb", "fsl,imx6sx";
 
-	backlight {
+	backlight1 {
 		compatible = "pwm-backlight";
 		pwms = <&pwm3 0 5000000>;
 		brightness-levels = <0 4 8 16 32 64 128 255>;
